# rake (>= 0.8.7), minitest (>= 2.0.2)
Description: Hoe is a rake/rubygems helper for project Rakefiles
 Hoe is a rake/rubygems helper for project Rakefiles. It helps you
 manage and maintain, and release your project and includes a dynamic
 plug-in system allowing for easy extensibility. Hoe ships with
 plug-ins for all your usual project tasks including rdoc generation,
 testing, packaging, and deployment.
 .\n See class rdoc for help. Hint: `ri Hoe` or any of the plugins listed
 below.
 .\n For extra goodness, see: http://seattlerb.rubyforge.org/hoe/Hoe.pdf

